.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Color: blue, green, red, white, yellow
Nationality: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
Sport: golf, parkour, basketball, skateboarding, handball
Cigar: bluemaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
Flower: tulip, amaryllis, dahlia, iris, daffodil
1. Nationality:british == Color:red
2. Nationality:swedish == Flower:dahlia
3. Nationality:danish == Sport:skateboarding
4. Color:green is on the left of Color:white
5. Color:green == Sport:parkour
6. Cigar:pall-mall == Flower:amaryllis
7. Color:yellow == Cigar:dunhill
8. Sport:basketball is in the middle
9. Nationality:norwegian is on the far left
10. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Flower:tulip
11. Flower:daffodils is on the left or right of Cigar:dunhill
12. Cigar:bluemaster == Sport:golf
13. Nationality:german == Cigar:prince
14. Nationality:norwegian is on the left or right of Color:blue
15. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Sport:handball

.:: Answer ::.
